{"word":"λῆμψις","slug":"λῆμψις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λῆμψις, εως, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λείπω\">λείπω</a></el>] <b>receiving,</b> in commercial imagery <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λόγος\">λόγος</a> δόσεως ϰαὶ λήμψεως</el> = record of outflow and inflow, debit and credit <b><a href='B:570 4:15'>Phil 4:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λήθη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:λήμψομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}